sect2.para:
CCCConfer (
http://www.cccconfer.org/index1.aspx
) provides Synchronous conferencing services for the 108 campuses of the California Community College system. The service initially used Wimba products but now has changed to Elluminate Live.

Etudes NG should be singled out and analyzed in more detail. Originally a project developed by an Instructor at Foothill College as an alternative to the big commercial Learning Management Systems; Etudes morphed into a Sakai derivative driven by a Consortium (
http://www.etudesproject.org/
) with a current membership of 23 community colleges.
